#: ../../developer/services/qrexec2.rst:103 e13c15c5e7b9477783e893a7ca56de2f
msgid ""
"Be very careful when coding and adding a new RPC service! Any vulnerability "
"in a RPC server can be fatal to security of the target VM!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/services/qrexec2.rst:105 a6a2f175512940ab82aac5eac5624544
